snippet.title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Episodes
snippet.description:
“Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Episodes”, is the official YouTube channel for the world's longest running daily family comedy show ‘Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah’. This show is a one stop destination for your daily dose of happiness, positivity, laughter & refreshing humour with your favorite TV Show. The channel has been created by the creator of show Asit Kumarr Modi and contains exclusive Episodes for our fans across the globe!

SUBSCRIBE to keep yourself updated with the latest on TMKOC, watch your favourite episodes and have a hearty laugh..!
